⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Ishamael
node WOT · WOT · ⟦Ishamael:WOT:1f1471⟧

WHO   — Ishamael — the Betrayer of Hope, first of the Forsaken
WHAT  — The first and greatest of the Forsaken, a philosopher of despair later reborn as Moridin.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: the Shadow — the Forsaken, servants of the Dark One  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — He is the Dragon's truest mirror and oldest enemy, embodying the Shadow's claim that the struggle is endless.
HOW   — Less fully imprisoned than his fellows, he works across Ages and rebirths to torment the Dragon.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  He named the war meaningless, and made himself its endless wound.

